					<div class="artCont">
						<div class="text"><h3 class="pd-title pd-summary-title" style="margin: 10px 0px;padding: 10px 0px;">项目简介</h3><p></p><p></p><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">健康是1，其他的是0，没有“1”的“0” 是没有任何意义的。</span></span><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">偏远山区的孩子们，一旦在健康方面出现问题，家庭的各项发展指标就被拉到负增长的局面；从小培养健康意识和良好生活习惯，对于孩子们的成长很重要。通过我们的努力，让孩子们润物细无声地健康成长，减少因健康问题带给一个家庭的悲伤，将是多么美好的事情。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;"><img src="https://cdn1.riceimg.com/editupload/201712/29/1514533580764420.jpg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">甘肃张家川县是国定贫困县，该项目的实施地——梁山乡梁山村地处三县交界，距离县城40公里山路，交通不便，经济发展缓慢，家庭中的主要劳动力全部外出打工创收。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">2011年新办的一所学前教育服务中心，也是我乡第一所，从刚开始的20名儿童，占地200平方米，如今发展到370名，占地面积1000平方米。时至目前，已经坚持了6年多时间，总计为500多名儿童提供了服务，留守儿童数占总服务儿童的80%以上，最早的一批儿童已经在读小学三年级，2016年该服务中心更名为“家乐幼儿园”。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">全园教职工10人，是一个年轻、活泼、积极向上的优秀团队。专职教师都是三十岁以下的年轻教师，有良好的职业道德，她们热爱孩子，有着孜孜不倦的敬业精神和创新的教学模式。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;"><img src="https://cdn1.riceimg.com/editupload/201712/29/1514533598590513.jpg"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">经过9月份中心马存俊、郭小龙与该乡村幼教负责人马志军讨论了留守儿童在幼教过程中遇到的问题，了解到这些儿童中隔代监护的比较多，普遍自理意识和能力都比较低下，个人卫生不注意，也没有养成习惯；加之经济条件差，没有做好保暖措施，有些孩子的手脸因为寒冷被冻出皲裂和紫红的颜色。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">而作为乡村幼教机构还没有能力解决这些问题。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;">综合相关因素，我们通过筛选，选出一批家庭较为贫困的儿童，计划为他/她们提供冬季个人卫生用品和针对所有儿童良好个人习惯的培育工作。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-top: